{{zh-forms|[[皇帝]][[不]][[急]]，[[急]][[死]][[太监]]|[[皇帝不急，急死太監]]}}
==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: huángdì bù jí, jí sĭ tàijiàn
===Etymology===
Literally: the [[emperor]] is not worried, but the [[eunuch]]s are worried to death
===Proverb===
# the person involved is calm and collected, but observers are very worried
